    <release version="2023.7.1-next" date="2023-07-01">
      <description translatable="no">
        <p>- Added support for the following tag properties: BPM, Composer, Description, Publisher, ISRC</p>
        <p>- Improved album art design and added support for managing back cover art and exporting album art</p>
